headline: Starbucks Under Strain as CEO Brian Niccol Confronts Growing Missteps
summary: Douglas and Lee analyze why Starbucks’ CEO is their leading candidate for worst CEO of the year, pointing to strategic errors, operational setbacks, and a shifting consumer landscape.
